File ...</div></span><div id="docs-ml-header-edit-button-aria-label" style="display:none;">Ó╣üÓĖüÓ╣ēÓ╣äÓĖé</div><span class="docs-ml-header-item docs-ml-header-edit-button" aria-labelledby="docs-ml-header-edit-button-aria-label" role="button" tabindex="0"><div class="docs-ml-header-icon-container"><div class="docs-ml-icon docs-ml-header-icon"><div class="docs-ml-img-container docs-ml-img docs-ml-edit-icon"></div></div></div></span></div><div class="app-container"><div class="doc-container"><div class="doc"><div class="doc-content" style="background-color:#ffffff;max-width:468pt;padding:72pt 72pt 72pt 72pt"><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Courier&quot;;font-style:normal"># TYSM Faucet V3 ŌĆö Base Sepolia End-to-End Testing Checklist<br><br>**Status:** Pre-Mainnet Staging Verification &nbsp;<br>**Target Network:** Base Sepolia (Chain ID: `84532`) &nbsp;<br>**Purpose:** Validate off-chain EIP-712 authorization signing, Neynar cast verification, Redis deduplication, and on-chain `claimWithSignature` execution before mainnet deployment.<br><br>---<br><br>## 1. E2E Testing Checklist<br><br>- [ ] **Contract Deployment**<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Deploy `MockTYSM` (ERC-20 test token) to Base Sepolia.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Deploy `TYSMFaucetV3` with three constructor arguments: `&lt;MOCK_TYSM_ADDRESS&gt;`, `&lt;TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_ADDRESS&gt;`, and `&lt;OWNER_ADDRESS&gt;`.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Transfer `MockTYSM` tokens into the `TYSMFaucetV3` contract balance.<br>- [ ] **Backend Environment Configuration**<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Set Base Sepolia environment variables on Vercel (Preview/Development) and local `.env`.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Verify `TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_PRIVATE_KEY` corresponds to `TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_ADDRESS`.<br>- [ ] **Happy Path Verification**<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Post a public Farcaster cast containing `#tysmfaucet` or an approved marker.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Send `POST /api/claim-authorization` request with valid `fid`, `wallet`, `castHash`, and `chainId: 84532`.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Receive HTTP 200 response with `{ deadline, nonce, signature }`.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Confirm `tysm:v3:used_cast:&lt;castHash&gt;` key is stored in Upstash Redis.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Call `claimWithSignature(deadline, nonce, signature)` on Base Sepolia from `&lt;CLAIMING_WALLET&gt;`.<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Confirm `MockTYSM` tokens are received in `&lt;CLAIMING_WALLET&gt;`.<br>- [ ] **Negative Path Verification**<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Reused `castHash` rejected by backend (`share_already_used`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Reused signature/nonce rejected on-chain (`"Authorization already used"`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Wallet / FID mismatch rejected by backend (`wallet_fid_mismatch`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Missing marker in cast rejected by backend (`share_not_found`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Expired deadline rejected on-chain (`"Signature expired"`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Denylisted wallet rejected by backend (`not_eligible`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Paused contract reverts claim on-chain (`"Faucet is paused"`).<br> &nbsp;- [ ] Domain / signer mismatch reverts on-chain (`"Invalid signer"`).<br><br>---<br><br>## 2. Environment Variables Setup (Placeholders Only)<br><br>Configure these keys in your local development environment and Vercel project settings for Base Sepolia:<br><br>```text<br>TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_CONTRACT_ADDRESS=&lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_V3_CONTRACT&gt;<br>TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_ADDRESS=&lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_ADDRESS&gt;<br>TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_PRIVATE_KEY=&lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_PRIVATE_KEY&gt;<br>NEYNAR_API_KEY=&lt;NEYNAR_API_KEY&gt;<br>UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=&lt;UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL&gt;<br>UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=&lt;UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN&gt;<br></span></p><h2 style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:18pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:18pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">3. Deployment Steps on Base Sepolia</span></h2><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Note:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Adjust contract paths to match the actual deployment project layout.</span></p><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Step 3.1: Deploy MockTYSM Token</span></h3><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Deploy a mock ERC-20 token (18 decimals) to serve as TYSM on Base Sepolia:</span></p><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Courier&quot;;font-style:normal">forge create --rpc-url &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL&gt; \<br> &nbsp;--private-key &lt;DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY&gt; \<br> &nbsp;src/MockTYSM.sol:MockTYSM<br></span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:italic">Record the resulting contract address as &lt;MOCK_TYSM_ADDRESS&gt;.</span></p><h3 style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Step 3.2: Deploy TYSMFaucetV3</span></h3><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Deploy TYSMFaucetV3 passing all three required constructor arguments (_tysm, _signer, _owner):</span></p><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Courier&quot;;font-style:normal">forge create --rpc-url &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL&gt; \<br> &nbsp;--private-key &lt;DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY&gt; \<br> &nbsp;src/TYSMFaucetV3.sol:TYSMFaucetV3 \<br> &nbsp;--constructor-args &lt;MOCK_TYSM_ADDRESS&gt; &lt;TYSM_V3_SEPOLIA_SIGNER_ADDRESS&gt; &lt;OWNER_ADDRESS&gt;<br></span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:italic">Record the resulting contract address as &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_V3_CONTRACT&gt;.</span></p><h2 style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:18pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:18pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">4. Fund the Faucet</span></h2><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Transfer or mint MockTYSM tokens into the deployed TYSMFaucetV3 contract:</span></p><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Courier&quot;;font-style:normal"># Example: Transfer 1,000,000 MockTYSM tokens to the faucet contract<br>cast send &lt;MOCK_TYSM_ADDRESS&gt; \<br> &nbsp;"transfer(address,uint256)" &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_V3_CONTRACT&gt; 1000000000000000000000000 \<br> &nbsp;--rpc-url &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL&gt; \<br> &nbsp;--private-key &lt;DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY&gt;<br></span></p><p style="padding:0;margin:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">Verify the contract's token balance:</span></p><p style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;padding-left:0;font-size:11pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Courier&quot;;font-style:normal">cast call &lt;MOCK_TYSM_ADDRESS&gt; \<br> &nbsp;"balanceOf(address)(uint256)" &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_V3_CONTRACT&gt; \<br> &nbsp;--rpc-url &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL&gt;<br></span></p><h2 style="padding-top:0pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:18pt;padding-bottom:11.2pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:18pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">5. Set Vercel Environment Variables</span></h2><ol class="lst-kix_list_1-0 start" start="1" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span>Navigate to </span><span style="font-weight:700">Vercel Dashboard</span><span>&nbsp;&gt; </span><span style="font-weight:700">Project Settings</span><span>&nbsp;&gt; </span><span style="font-weight:700">Environment Variables</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span>Assign the following values for </span><span style="font-weight:700">Preview</span><span>&nbsp;and </span><span style="font-weight:700">Development</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;environments:</span></li></ol><ul class="lst-kix_list_2-1 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:60pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="