gin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause 2:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Upstash Redis credentials or NEYNAR_API_KEY are missing or invalid in the runtime environment.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Resolution:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Check application logs for [claim-authorization] missing or invalid app config or signer_mismatch. Ensure lower-case address equality.</span></li></ul><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">wallet_fid_mismatch (HTTP 400)</span></h3><ul class="lst-kix_list_4-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;The requested wallet address is not present in Neynar's verified ETH addresses or custody address for the fid.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Resolution:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Confirm account link on Farcaster/Warpcast or verify via Neynar User API endpoint.</span></li></ul><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">share_not_found (HTTP 400)</span></h3><ul class="lst-kix_list_5-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Cast hash does not exist, author FID differs, cast is older than 7 days (SHARE_MAX_AGE_SECONDS), or lacks approved hashtag markers.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Resolution:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Inspect cast content on Neynar. Ensure #tysmfaucet or tysm-faucet is present in cast body.</span></li></ul><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">share_already_used (HTTP 400)</span></h3><ul class="lst-kix_list_6-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Redis key tysm:v3:used_cast:&lt;castHash&gt; exists.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Resolution:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Create a fresh test cast for new claim authorizations. Delete key manually in Redis CLI for isolated reset if necessary.</span></li></ul><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">"Invalid signer" (On-chain Revert)</span></h3><ul class="lst-kix_list_7-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause 1:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;The EIP-712 domain name (TYSMFaucetV3), version (1), chainId (84532), or verifyingContract address does not match contract domain.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause 2:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;On-chain signer variable differs from off-chain signing key account address.</span></li><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Resolution:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;Query contract getter signer() on-chain via cast call &lt;BASE_SEPOLIA_V3_CONTRACT&gt; "signer()(address)" and confirm match with API configuration.</span></li></ul><h3 style="padding-top:12pt;margin:0;color:#000000;font-weight:700;padding-left:0;font-size:14pt;padding-bottom:12pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;line-height:1.0;text-align:left;padding-right:0"><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:14pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">"Authorization already used" (On-chain Revert)</span></h3><ul class="lst-kix_list_8-0 start" style="padding:0;margin:0"><li style="padding:0;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;line-height:1.0;margin-right:0;margin-left:30pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left"><span style="font-weight:700">Cause:</span><span style="color:#000000;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;font-size:11pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;;font-style:normal">&nbsp;The nonce has 